Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎  我的士兵們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備向前  進！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左40度主炮發射  準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離400
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝彈  彈種  定型炸藥彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織賀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這鐵箱裡關了三天了  在洗澡前怎麼能死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準完成  發射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜  向後方部隊傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經擊破一輛  叫他們跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利西婭  你來掩護安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在閃爍  但放心那不是打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3點方…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣紙  賣簽
